ZH: 阁楼是位于房屋顶部的空间。
EN: An attic is a space located on the top of a house.
ZH: 这个房子有一个宽敞的阁楼。
EN: This house has a spacious attic.
ZH: 我把我的旧书存在阁楼上。
EN: I store my old books in the attic.
ZH: 阁楼通常用来储存物品。
EN: Attics are typically used for storage purposes.
ZH: 我喜欢在阁楼上看书。
EN: I enjoy reading books in the attic.
ZH: 他在阁楼上搭建了一个小工作室。
EN: He set up a small studio on the attic.
ZH: 阁楼里闷热的空气使我感到不舒服。
EN: The hot air in the attic makes me uncomfortable.
ZH: 我在阁楼上发现了一只老鼠。
EN: I found a mouse in the attic.
ZH: 阁楼上的阳光透过窗户洒进来。
EN: Sunlight streams into the attic through the windows.
ZH: 我昨晚在梦中来到了一个阁楼。
EN: I dreamt of being in an attic last night.
ZH: 阁楼里的灯光昏暗而柔和。
EN: The lighting in the attic is dim and soft.
ZH: 我最喜欢阁楼上的壁炉了。
EN: I love the fireplace in the attic the most.
